<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 col-centered">
    <div class="x_panel tile">
      <div class="x_title">
        <h2>Collaborate to ---Name of the project---</h2>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="x_content">
        <br>
        <p>You are about to collaborate to a project and help us change the world ! We remind you that there is no small contribution ! Please fill the following fields to complete your donation.</p>
        <p>Do not forget to tell us if you are interested in the rewards !</p>
        <p>And we remind you that 5% of your contribution will be offered to one of our partner companies to support their actions of planting trees and create green areas in the work places !</p>
        <br>
        <form class="form-horizontal form-label-left input_mask">
          <label class="col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12">Amount</label>
          <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
            <input class="form-control" id="contribution_amount" required="required" placeholder="$" type="text">
          </div>
        </form>
        <br>
        <p>I do want to recieve the rewards. <%= check_box :dispatchable, class: "form-control" %></p>
        <br>
        <p>Please, upload a document proving that the amount indicated above has been transferred to the following bank account:</p>
        <p><b>Bank: </b></p>
        <p><b>Account Number: </b></p>
        <p><b>Account Owner: </b></p>
        <br>
        <form action="form_upload.html">
          <input type="file" name="proof_paiement" accept=".pdf|image/*">
        </form>
        <div class="ln_solid" style="margin: 10px"></div>
        <p style="text-align: center;">
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-default" style="text-align: center;">Collaborate</button>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>